These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, fantasy, mystery
4 different games are played: scrabble, domino, backgammon, snooker
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, sunflower, balloon-flower, aconite
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, jet-ski, tram, trike
1. the person who growssunflower is the person playing snooker##1
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is between the person watching fantasy movies and the person watching mystery movies##2
3. the person who growssunflower is the person driving the bus##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
5. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
6. the person driving the tram is the person watching fantasy movies##1
7. the person playing domino is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
8. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far right##1
9. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | mystery   | adventure  | fantasy  |
| Game   | domino    | snooker    | scrabble      | backgammon    |
| Flower   | aconite | sunflower | balloon-flower | daffodil |
| Transport     | trike  | bus       | jet-ski    | tram     |

