.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, august, may, december
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, adventure, scientific, western
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, watermelon, broccoli, avocado
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, lacrosse, swimming, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far right##1
3. the person eating avocado is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
5. the person watching western movies is between the person eating broccoli and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
6. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person watching western movies and the person eating avocado##2
7. the person eating asparagus is on the far right##1
8. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
9. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Birthday         | december | august    | may  | june    |
| Movie-Genre   | action      | adventure  | western  | scientific |
| Food           | avocado      | broccoli       | watermelon      | asparagus       |
| Sport         | lacrosse    | water-polo | swimming | ice-hockey |

