The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, roller, subway
1. the person watching documentary movies is the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
6. the person watching action movies is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
7. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
8. the person who growslily is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
9. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person who growssunflower and the person watching action movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Flower        | aconite | sunflower     | lily   | tulip     |
