.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, mechanic, police-officer, teacher
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, collecting, camping, hiking
City: nizza, prague, boston, miami
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rugby, soccer, volleyball
 1. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's hobby is hiking is the fisherman##1
 3. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person traveling to prague##1
 6. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 7. the person who's hobby is collecting is the police-officer##1
 8. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 9. the fisherman is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
10. the mechanic is between the person traveling to nizza and the teacher##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Job           | fisherman  | teacher | mechanic     | police-officer |
| Hobby   | hiking | cooking  | camping | collecting       |
| City           | prague       | miami    | boston      | nizza           |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | rugby   | volleyball   | soccer         |

