.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-5::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, garlic, lemon, peach
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, d&b, soul, punk
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, oliveros, chaman, bolivar
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, ice-hockey, sailing, weightlifting
 1. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
 2. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1
 3. the fan of soul is the person eating garlic##1
 4. the fan of soul is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 5. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 6. the person eating lemon is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
 7. the fan of punk is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
 8. the fan of d&b is the oliveros-smoker##1
 9. the person eating lemon is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the havana-smoker##2
10. the chaman-smoker is the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | garlic         | lemon         | asparagus     | peach      |
| Music-Genre           | soul | punk | trance    | d&b     |
| Cigar   | havana      | chaman       | bolivar    | oliveros       |
| Sport         | basketball     | sailing       | weightlifting | ice-hockey |

