The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, funk, jazz, punk
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, dutch, polish, turkish
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, fishing, card-games, traveling
1. the fan of folk is between the person who's hobby is traveling and the fan of jazz##2
2. the farmhouse house is between the fan of folk and the turkish##2
3. the polish is between the person who's hobby is fishing and the dutch##2
4. the cottage house is on the left of the dutch##1
5. the polish is the polish##1
6. the dutch is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
7. the dutch is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
8. the fan of jazz is on the far right##1
9. the fan of funk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| House           | cottage | farmhouse | ranch-style  | victorian |
| Music-Genre   | funk      | punk       | folk     | jazz      |
| Nationality   | turkish   | dutch      | polish   | chinese   |
| Hobby         | card-games   | traveling    | writing | fishing   |

