.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-7::.
4 different pets are kept: frog, goat, cat, rabbit
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, dubstep, metal, soul
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, tennis, skateboarding, cycling
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, subway, train
 1. the person driving the train is on the right of the fan of blues##1
 2. the owner of the goat is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 3. the fan of dubstep is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person driving the subway##2
 4. the fan of metal is the person driving the train##1
 5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 6. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 7. the person who's sport is golf is the person driving the airplane##1
 8. the fan of soul is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
10. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Pet   | cat | goat | frog  | rabbit  |
| Music-Genre   | blues       | metal   | dubstep | soul    |
| Sport   | golf   | skateboarding   | cycling | tennis |
| Transport     | airplane    | train   | bike    | subway  |

