 6. the person who likes lavender is on the far left##1
 7. the designer is on the left of the fisherman##1
 8. the person who likes amber is on the far right##1
 9. the accountant is between the social-worker and the modern house##2
10. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |
