 4. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
 5. the owner of the goldfish is between the owner of the goat and the owner of the hamster##2
 6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person who growslily##1
 7. the person who growsrose is the davidoff-smoker##1
 8. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the hamster is the person driving the train##1
10. the person who growszinnia is the siglo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |
| Cigar        | dunhill  | davidoff | siglo     | bluemaster     |
| Pet         | hamster | goldfish | goat     | guinea-pig |
